dct_title_s: Mexico and the United States and their mutual relations
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Shows railways and canals. Detatched from Abbot, Gorham D., Mexico, and the United States; their mutual relations and common interests. New York, Putnam, 1869. 972 A12m.
